lyTime":"2019-09-30T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026e71eec62ff67a3227c1c71403ee4365afe129","tid":1604143,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"推進香港民主自由和「一國兩制」行穩致遠，符合包括香港親中派在內中國國家的戰略利益；香港一些政客執意推動取消區議會選舉，必將損害中國在港的利益，搬起石頭砸自己的腳。香港人民絕不會坐視中國勢力肆意干預香港事務，我們敦促那些親中派政客立刻停止取消區議會選舉的玩火把戲，否則必將引火焚身，玩火自焚。"},{"pid":"32da50aab2e2e694cc508e5b91b7c8126b5222fa","tid":1604143,"uid":247311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"血債只能血償<br />\n不過勝選可以將更多賣港賊推上斷頭台<br />\n所以投票取得勝利，一舉清算狗賊<br />\n冇選舉就加速清算支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6234b3221c7f4ca5b9e57d2e491ff7eb87d92c6","tid":1604143,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4ef03fb73388de24625ec5d4bd6a0755412836c","tid":1604143,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d1c1a31b92f47ec5a28ef28d547e360b19c809","tid":1604143,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"即使最激進的「勇武派」高舉「血債票償」旗幟，誓用選票懲罰建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我冇聽過激進勇武派仲會同你玩選舉遊戲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"有激進派反而主張射落海/投建制攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"個d鬼黎"}]}